game.name: Supermarket Supplier
game.description: The supermarkets in this town need merchandise and only you can provide it to them. Drive your trucks and deliver packages in the trailer. Each store will take the crates it needs and will pay you good money for them. You can use the cash you earn to buy some cool upgrades that will help you improve your vehicle and go even further on the map. Your goal is to reach the end. Have a lot of fun playing Supermarket Supplier!
